1. *Pio* je pivo uz večeru. (He drank beer with dinner.)
2. Njegov sin *pi* pivo sa prijateljima. (His son is drinking beer with friends.)
3. Ona je *pila* čaj svako jutro. (She used to drink tea every morning.)
4. *Pij* vodu umesto soka. (Drink water instead of juice.)
5. Oni su *pili* vino tokom proslave. (They were drinking wine during the celebration.)